name: Nav - Fill
heading: nav-fill
description: Documentation and examples for how to use Bootstrap's included navigation components.
usage: Force your .nav’s contents to extend the full available width one of two modifier classes. To proportionately fill all available space with your .nav-items, use .nav-fill. Notice that all horizontal space is occupied, but not every nav item has the same width.
